{
  "chapter": 83,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十三回\"有情谷\"讲述了芮玮、白燕、高莫静三人在瀑布冲落后的遭遇。芮玮和白燕被冲到谷底潭边，高莫静失踪。芮玮在绝望中发现身处万仞高峰围成的死谷地，白燕醒后因能与芮玮永伴而欣喜若狂。芮玮发现白燕身上的香囊（碧绿色小叶子制成），暗中藏起以控制摄魂针之毒。芮玮在瀑布下潜水中发现高莫静的绣鞋，穿入瀑布后的山洞找到高莫静——她容貌被岩石划伤，性情大变，拒绝芮玮接近。高莫静赠芮玮四照神功和海渊剑谱，芮玮以七叶果交换为其复容。芮玮回到潭边后对白燕态度冷淡，质问摄魂针之事。白燕取谷名为\"有情谷\"，暗示可能怀孕。本章展现了高莫静毁容后的自尊与孤僻，芮玮对两位女性的复杂情感，以及摄魂针之谜的推进。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦？她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉，连水都不容我，老天啊，你要我活着有什么意思？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们死了没有？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "死到没死，只是咱们俩人要在一起生活一辈子啦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那再好不过，我本来就要命你和我一起生活一辈子嘛。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "别太早高兴，你先看看四周环境。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "怎么办，咱们要老死此地了！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "可不是吗，所以我说你不要太早高兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老天安排得太好了……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "相公，我怕这生不能把你心收在我身旁，现在我不怕了，老天安排咱们永不分离，我怎不高兴！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不穿，你要穿自己做吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "不穿总要弄点吃的吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "就吃它肉，真对不起，咱们既穿它又要吃它。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好主意，我来弄，你等着看我手艺如何？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "看怎行，要尝啊。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你放心，会让你吃饱的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你怎么啦，费这大劲开两个洞作什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "睡啊？咱们总不能每天睡在草地上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那一个就成，何必开两个，别吃饱没事做。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "你睡一个，我睡一个，一个穴洞怎够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们还要分开睡，而且分得那么远？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪？这大的雷声竟盖不住说话声音！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "前辈贵……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你？高姐姐……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮……芮大哥……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你没死！你没死……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不要过来，不错，我没死，但我不再见你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我看到你花容毁了，这有什么关系，难道为了脸上几处伤痕就不见老朋友了吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不准你走来就不准，听到没有！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我不走来，咱们就这样说话可好？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要说什么，说吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你可知我身上有枚七叶果？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你想用七叶果替我复容是不？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "这七叶果研碎成计粉外敷，功能生肌拔毒，你脸上被岩石划破的伤口只要涂上，即可复原不留一点疤痕。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不用了，我容貌已毁没什要紧，何必浪费一枚珍贵的七叶果。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不是在客气，七叶果还是留着吧，据我想：你冒险盗七叶果的用意定是用来给令堂医治脑病，好好保存留给她老人家服用。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "你大概没察看目下咱们的境遇，此生脱困甚难，这果子再也送不到家母那里，与其糟蹋不用，给你复容有何不可，你不必推辞，我这就着手医治。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到底听不听我的话？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这个你拿着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "四照神功是姐姐的东西，还请你自己保管。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "二妹送你的能收，我送的就不能收吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "不是我不收，我想人家既不收我的东西，我有何脸收人家的东西？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你定要我收下七叶果复容吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "这是我一点心意，咱们以物易物，两人皆都收下可好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你把七叶果抛过来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "此果我暂代保管，哪一年脱困后再奉还。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "那四照神功我也代你保管。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁要你保管，你不知我赠你四照神功的用意吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "姐姐也该知我赠果的用意。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我是不愿糟蹋七叶果，你练了四照神功的用处极大。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "七叶果替你复容怎说糟蹋，你要不用它复容，抱歉，我决不会修习四照神功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你可知不习四照神功，此生无法与如梦大师相抗吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我知道得很清楚，而且太阳门将再出世，与其对抗，这四照神功实是月形门弟子莫大的裨益。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这么说，你练四照神功从此承认月形门弟子，有义务除去月形门世敌太阳门吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "这个当然。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，我用七叶果复容就是，其实复不复容……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "text": "我略通医术，这复容一事可否让我效劳？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你想接近我，我坚辞不准，并非我有什么古怪，此生我想孤独一人不再见任何人，你去吧，复容一事我自会弄，用不着你费心。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_mo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "高莫静",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这洞中的覃菌就是最好的食物。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你潜到哪里去了？害得我差点没有急死！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "没怎么，我累了要歇歇。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "抱抱我，今天你不抱我，以后没机会了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "天天生活在一起，还怕机会不多？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "你怕我闻到你身上臭味，为何不将我背上的摄魂针除去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你怎知摄魂针的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "买影人三种针，因人而定，一日追魂针，二曰失魂针，三日摄魂针，在下身受正是第三种。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁……谁……告诉你的……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "秦百龄。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他对我无影门怎么这等清楚……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "小姐，处此绝境摄魂针该取出来了吧？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我倒没认为此地为绝境，我给它取了个名字叫有情谷，咱们在此结情，有情两字不正恰当？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你记得昨天咱们……我……我可能怀了孕……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_bai_yan",
      "text": "怀什么孕，不会那么巧。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yan",
      "speaker_name": "白燕",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你希望我生男的还是女的？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    }
  ],
